snippet.textDisplay:
please help me sir 
 Mera Naam kundan kumar hai mai purbi champarn se ek chhoti se village chakia jitaura gopalpur se vilom karta hu 
mera bhaiya ka awash nahin mila hai aur payment list me naam hai  sahaek 20000 gus many raha hai jo ki mere pass nahin 
block me bhi gay lekin kuchh nahin hua 
suchna adhikar ko bhi abedan diye fhir bhi 
kuchh nahin hua  mai ek garib pariwar se hu paswan jati ka hu maine bahut taran ki kosis karli lekin kuchh nahin please aap hi help kar sakte hai please ek baar aye aur ye sari baat ko puri kare mere jaise kitne sare vekti ko nahin mila hai bas ek hi karan 20000.25000 ka gus many raha hai
